snippet.title: Breakfast At Cemetery Trailer
snippet.description:
Breakfast at Cemetery is a QWOP style game where your task, as a skeleton, is to eat breakfast as quickly as possible.

Available NOW at http://dddwares.itch.io/breakfast-at-cemetery 
http://depressingdrawers.tumblr.com/
